Description: Move configure.in to configure.ac
 Autoconf has long deprecated configure.in, but version 2.0 will make it
 incompatible. This patch anticipates that, as per
 https://lists.gnu.org/archive/html/automake/2013-05/msg00049.html
Forwarded: yes
Author: Rowan Thorpe <rowan@rowanthorpe.com>
Last-Update: 2013-10-04
--- a/INSTALL
+++ b/INSTALL
@@ -19,8 +19,8 @@
